      <h2 class="uc-section-title">Pager</h2>
      <p>You can create a pager by specifying the <code>uc-pager</code> class.</p>

      <div class="doc-component-box" id="c-1">
        <h3>1. Basic</h3>
        <p>Create a basic pager.</p>

        <div class="doc-component-preview">
          <div class="uc-pager-unit">
            <ul class="uc-pager">
              <li class="_current"><span>1</span></li>
              <li><a href="#"><span>2</span></a></li>
              <li><a href="#"><span>3</span></a></li>
              <li><a href="#"><span>4</span></a></li>
              <li class="_ghost"><span>...</span></li>
              <li><a href="#"><span>10</span></a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="uc-code-unit">
<pre><code class="html">&lt;div class="uc-pager-unit"&gt;
  &lt;ul class="uc-pager"&gt;
    &lt;li class="_current"&gt;&lt;span&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#"&gt;&lt;span&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#"&gt;&lt;span&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
